hadiths[102]{hadithnumber,text}:
565,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka haar gir pada. wo uski talash mein peechey reh gaeen (is wajeh sey qafla bhi ruk gaya). Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaey aur logon key rukney ka baais bin janey par un par narazi ka izhar farmaya. (chunkey us maqam par wuzu key liye pani mojud nahin tha) chunanche Allah Taala ney tayammum ki ijazat nazil farma di. (Sabab farmatey hain : ) us din hamney kandhon tak masah kiya. (uskey baad) Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaey aur kaha : mujhey malum na tha ke tum is qadr baaise barkat ho."
566,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath kandhon tak tayammum kiya."
567,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey liye zamin masjid aur pakizgi hasil karney ka zariya bana di gaee hai.
568,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) sey eik haar aariyatan (udhaar) liya (safar key doran main eik maqam par) wo haar gum ho gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chand afrad us ko talash karney key liye bhejey. (us doran mein) namaz ka waqt ho gaya to un afrad ney wuzu kiye baghair namaz padh li. (kyonkey unkey paas pani nahin tha)  jab wo (haar talash kar key) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye to unhoney us chiz ki shikayat ki. tab tayammum ki aayat nazil ho gaee. Hazrat Usaid bin Huzer (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah Taala aap ko jazaae-khair ata farmaaey ! aap par jab bhi koi mushkil aai, Allah Taala ney aap ko to us (mushkil) sey najat dey di aur is mein musalmanon key liye koi barkat inayat farma di."
569,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : agar mujhey janabat (sambhog ke bad napaaki ki haalat) ki haalat pesh aa jaey aur pani na miley (to kya karun)? Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : namaz na padh (jab pani milega to ghusl kar key qaza namaz padhna). Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhuma) ney kaha : Ameerul Momineen ! kya aap ko yad nahin jab main aur aap dono eik lashkar mein they. hamen ghusl ki hajat pesh aai aur pani na mila (us waqt bhi) aap ney to namaz nahin padhi thi, mainey zamin par lot pot ho kar namaz padh li thi. phir jab main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to ye waqia arz kiya, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey to itna hi kafi tha.   aur (ye keh kar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dono haath zamin par maarey, phir un mein phunk maari aur chehrey aur dono hatheliyon par masah kiya."
570,"Hazrat Hukm aur Hazrat Salma bin Kuheil sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu Ufaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey tayammum ka masla daryaft kiya, to unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ko is tarah karney ka hukm diya tha. ye keh kar unhoney apney dono haath zamin par maarey, phir unhen jhaada aur unhen apney chehrey par pher liya. Hukm ney kaha : aur apney haathon par pher liya. aur Salma bin Kuheil ney kaha : aur apni kohniyon par pher liya."
571,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath tayammum kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney musalmanon ko hukm diya to unhoney mitti par haath maarey aur haath mein mitti nahin pakdi, phir eik baar chehrey par haath pher liye, phir dobara zamin par haath maarey aur haathon par masah kiya."
572,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney main eik aadmi ka sar zakhmi ho gaya. uskey baad (eik din) usey ehtilaam ho gaya. (usney Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum sey masla poochha)  to usey nahaney ka hukm diya gaya. usney ghusl kiya to (sardi ki shiddat ki wajeh sey) bimar ho gaya aur (usi bimari sey) faut ho gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko us waqiey ki ittilaa hui to farmaya : unhoney usey qatl kar diya, Allah unhen halak karey. kya poochh lena la-ilmi ka ilaj nahin? Hazrat Ata (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : hamein riwayat pahunchi hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : kaash! wo baqi jism dho leta aur sar ko rehney deta jahan usey zakham tha."
573,"Ummul-mominin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye ghusl ka pani rakha to aap ney ghusle-janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat ka ghusl) kiya (pehley) baaein hath sey bartan ko jhuka kar daain haath par pani dala aur teen baar apney dono haath dhoey. phir apni sharmgah par pani dala (aur istinja kiya), phir zamin par haath ragdaa (aur saaf kar liya) phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani dala. teen baar Chehra Mubarak dhoya, aur teen baar bazu dhoey. phir baqi jism par pani baha liya. phir eik taraf ho kar dono paon dho liye."
574,"Hazrat Jamee bin Umer Taimi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main apni phuphi jaan aur khaala jaan key sath gaya. hum Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur un sey puchha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusle-janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat ka ghusl) key moqey par kiya tariqa ikhtiyar kartey they? unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) teen baar haathon par pani daltey they, uskey baad pani key bartan mein haath daltey , phir teen baar apna sar Mubarak dhotey , phir apney jism Mubarak par pani bahaatey. uskey baad namaz key liye tashrif ley jatey. lekin hum baal ghundhey huye honey ki wajeh sey paanch baar sar dhoti hain."
575,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein ghusle-janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat ka ghusl) key barey mein behes ho gaee to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main to apney sar par teen lap (pani) daalta hun."
576,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney un sey ghusle-janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat ka ghusl) key barey mein sawal kiya to unhoney farmaya : teen (lap pani sar par dalo). us shakhs ney kaha : merey baal bahut ziyada hain. Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baal tum sey ziyada they, aur wo tum sey ziyada pakizah they."
577,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main sard ilaqey mein rehta hun to ghusle-janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat ka ghusl) kaisey karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main to apney sar par teen lap daalta hun."
578,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke un sey eik aadmi ney sawal kiya : jab main junbi (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat mein) hun to (ghusl kartey waqt) sar par kitna pani dala karun? Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney sar Mubarak par teen lap (pani) dala kartey they. us shakhs ney kaha : merey baal lambey hain. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baal tujh sey ziyada they : aur ziyada pakizah they.
579,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusle-janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat ke ghusl) key baad wuzu nahin kartey they."
580,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusle-janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat ka ghusl) kartey they, phir merey ghusl karney sey pehley mujh sey (lipat kar) garmi hasil kartey they."
581,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko janabat(samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat) ki keyfiyat pesh aati thi, phir aap pani ko haath lagaey baghair so jatey they yahan tak key baad mein uth kar ghusl farma letey."
582,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) agar apni ehal (ghar-wali) sey qurbat ki zarurat mehsus farmatey to apni ye hajat puri kar letey, phir pani ko haath lagaey baghair usi haalat mein so jatey."
583,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) junbi (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat mein) hotey they, to pani ko haath lagaey baghair usi haalat mein so jatey they. Sufiyan kehtey hain ke eik din mainey is hadees ka zikr kiya to Ismail ney farmaya : ladkey ! is hadees ko kisi chiz sey mazbut karney ki zarurat hai."
584,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab nahaney ki hajat hoti aur aap (nahaaey baghair) sona chahtey to namaz wala wuzu kar letey they."
585,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya : jab hum mein sey koi shakhs haalate janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat mein) mein ho to kya wo so sakta hai? aap ney farmaya : haan, jab wuzu kar ley (to so jaey)."
586,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo raat ko junbi (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat mein) ho jatey they, phir sona chahtey they, to (masla poochhney par) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein hukm diya ke wuzu kar lein, phir so jaaeyn."
587,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs apni biwi key paas jaaey, phir dobara jana chahey to wuzu kar ley."
588,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tamam biwiyon key paas jaaney key baad eik hi ghusl kar letey they.
589,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye pani rakha, to aap ney eik hi raat mein tamam azwaaje-mutah'raat (paak biwiyon) Raziallahu anhu  sey muqaribat key baad (eik hi baar) ghusl kiya."
590,"Hazrat abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik raat tamam azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) Raziallahu anhu key paas gaey. aap un mein sey har eik key ghar mein ghusl kartey rahey. kisi ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap eik hi ghusl kyon nahin kar letey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is (tareeqey) mein safai, pakizgi aur tahaarat ziyada hai."
591,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab ghusl ki hajat hoti aur (usi doran mein) aap kuchh tanaawul farmana (khaana) chahtey to (khaney sey pehley) wuzu kar letey."
592,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey junbi (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat mein insan) key mutalliq sawal kiya gaya : kya wo so sakta hai ya kha pi sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan , jab wuzu kar ley, jis tarah namaz key liye wuzu hota hai."
593,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (haalate-janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki) mein) ghusl karney sey pehley (kuchh tanaawul farmana (khaana) chahtey to apney haath dho letey.
594,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Salma (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. unhoney (masaayel bayan kartey huye) farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khalaa mein jatey, qazaey-hajat (peshaab-paakhaane) sey farigh ho kar bahar tashrif latey to hamarey sath roti gosht bhi tanaawul farmatey aur Quran ki tilawat bhi kartey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko janabat key siwa koi chiz Quran (ki tilawat) sey rukawat nahin hoti thi."
595,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : junbi (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat mein insan) aur haaiza Quran na padhein."
596,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : junbi (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat mein insan) aur haaiza Quran mein sey kuchh na padhein.
597,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har baal key nichey janabat (samhog ke bad ki napaaki) hai, isliye baalon ko dho dalo aur jild ko saaf karo."
598,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanchon namaazein, Juma doosrey Jumey tak aur amanat ki adaegi unkey darmiyani gunahon ka kaffara hai. mainey arz kiya : amanat ki adaegi sey kya murad hai? farmaya : janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat mein insan) ka ghusl kyonkey har baal key nichey janabat (samhog ke bad ki napaaki) hai."
599,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney ghusle-janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat ke ghusl) mein jism ki baal barabar jagah bhi chhod di aur usey na dhoya, usey aag ka itna itna (bahut ziyada) azab diya jaeyga. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : isi wajeh sey mainey apney baalon sey dushmani ikhtiyar kar li. aap sar key baal kaat diya kartey they."
600,"Hazrat Ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Umme Sulem (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur masla puchha ke agar aurat ko khuwab mein wo kuchh nazar aaye jo mard ko nazar aata hai (to uska kya hukm hai)? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan, jab usey pani nazar aaye to usey ghusl karna chahiye. (Ummul-mominin ney farmaya) mainey kaha : (aey Umme Sulem ! ) tum ney aurton ko ruswa kar diya hai, bhala aurat ko bhi ehtilaam hota hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tera bhala ho ! phir uski aulad us sey mushabeh kyon hoti hai?"
601,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Umme Sulem (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey us aurat key barey mein sawal kiya jisey khuwab mein wo chiz nazar aaye jo mard ko nazar aaya karti hai? to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab usey ye chiz nazar aaye aur usey inzaal ho jaey (paani nikal jaey) to is par ghusl karna wajib hai. Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aisey bhi ho jata hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan, mard ka pani gaadhaa aur safed hota hai aur aurat ka pani patla aur zard hota hai. un dono mein sey jo bhi sabqat (badhat) ley jaey ya ghalib aa jaey, bacha us sey mushabeh (us par shakl mein) hota hai."
602,"Hazrat Khaula binte Hakeem (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha ke agar aurat khuwab mein wohi dekhey jo kuchh mard dekhta hai? to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is par ghusl farz nahin jab tak usey inzaal (paani ka nikalna) na ho. jis tarah mard par ghusl wajib nahin jab tak usey inzaal (paani ka nikalna) na ho."
603,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kiya, ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main sar key baalon ki mendhiyan mazbooti sey banati hun, to kya ghusle-janabat (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat ke ghusl) key liye unhen khola karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey yehi kafi hai ke sar par pani ki teen lappein dal ley, phir apney (purey jism) par pani baha ley, to paak ho jaaeygi. ya farmaya : bas to pak ho gaee."
604,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Umer (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ko malum huwa ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) apni khawatin ko hukm detey hain ke jab wo ghusl karen to sar (ki mendhiyan waghera) khol liya karen. Ummul-mominin ney farmaya : Abdullah bin Amr par tajjub hai ! (ke wo aurton ko ghusl key liye baal kholney ka hukm detey hain) wo unhen ye hukm kyon nahin dey detey ke apney sar mundwaa diya karen. main aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik hi bartan mein ghusl kartey they, main to is sey ziyada nahin karti thi ke sar par teen baar pani dal leti thi. (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey baal kholney ka hukm nahin detey they.)"
605,"Hazrat Hisham bin Zohra key azad karda ghulam Hazrat abu-Saaib (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs junbi (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat mein insan) ho to thehrey huye pani mein ghusl na karey. Abu-Saaib ney kaha : aey Abu-Hurera ! phir wo kya karey? Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : kisi chiz mein pani ley kar ghusl kar ley."
606,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik Ansari Sahaba key paas gaey aur usey bulwaayaa. wo (ghar sey) nikla to uskey sar sey pani key qatrey tapak rahey they. chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shayad hamney tujhey jaldi mein dal diya? usney kaha : ji haan, aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : jab tujhey (kisi wajeh sey) jaldi pad jaey (aur tujhey farigh honey sey pehley peechhey hatna padey) ya tujhey inzaal (iskhalan) na ho to tujh par ghusl farz nahin, sirf wuzu karna zaruri hai."
607,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pani (ka istimal (pani) key kharij hone) sey wajib hota hai."
608,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja (biwi) mohtarma Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab (mard aur aurat key (khatney) sharam-gaahen)  baham (aapas mein) mil jaeyn , to ghusl wajib ho jata hai. mainey aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye amal kiya to hamney ghusl kiya."
609,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Islam key ibtidaai daur mein rukhsat (chhoot) thi (ke jima (sambhog) ki surat mein jab tak inzaal (iskhalan) na ho, ghusl wajib nahin hota tha). baad mein hamein ghusl karney ka hukm dey diya gaya."
610,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab mard aurat ki chaar shaakhon key darmiyan bethey, phir koshish karey to ghusl wajib ho gaya."
611,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab khatney baham (aapas mein) mil jaeyn aur supari chhup jaey to ghusl wajib ho jata hai."
612,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs neend sey bedaar ho aur usey (jism ya kapdon par) geelaa pan  (mani) nazar aaye aur usey khuwab yad na ho, wo ghusl karey aur agar usey mehsus ho ke usney khuwab (mein ghusl wajib karney wala amal) dekha hai aur (bedaar honey par) geelaa pan nazar na aaye to is par koi ghusl nahin."
613,"Hazrat Abu-Samah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kiya ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat kiya karta tha. aap jab ghusl karna chahtey to farmatey : mujh sey rukh pher lo . main aap ki taraf peeth kar leta aur kapda phela kar aap ko parda kar deta."
614,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Naufal sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey (Sahaba kiram sey) sawal kiya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney safar mein nafl padhey hain? koi shakhs mujhey (ye masla) bataaney wala na mila . aakhir mujhey Umme-Haani binte Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anha) ney bataya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fateh Makka key saal (Makka Mukarrma) tashrif laye. aap ney hukm diya to aap par parda kiya gaya, chunanche aap ney ghusl kiya phir aath rakat nafl ada kiye."
615,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs khuley maidan mein ghusl na karey, na aisi chhat par ghusl karey jis par parda na ho sakey. agar wo kisi ko nahin dekhta to is par to nazar padti hai."
616,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs qazaey-hajat (peshaab-paakhaane) key liye jana chahta ho aur namaz khadi ho jaey to usey chahiye ke pehley hajat sey faraaghat hasil karey."
617,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah ney is baat sey mana farmaya ke aadmi peshab rokey huye namaz padhey."
618,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs us haal mein namaz key liye khada na ho ke usey peshab ya pakhane ki hajat ho.
619,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi musalman peshab ya pakhane ki hajat hotey huye (namaz key liye) khada na ho yahan tak key halka phulka ho jaaey (hajat sey farigh ho jaey)."
620,"Hazrat Fatima binte Abu Habish (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar khoon (jari rehney) ki shikayat ki. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to eik rag hai, tum khayal rakha karo, jab tumhara haiz shuru ho jaaey to namaz na padho. jab haiz khatam ho jaey to ghusl kar lo, phir haiz (key khatam honey sey haiz) key shuru honey tak namaz ada karo."
621,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Fatima binte Abu Habish (Raziallahu anha) Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey istihaza ki shikayat hai, main to paak hi nahin hoti. to kya main namaz ko(bilkul) chhod dun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin, ye to eik rag hai, ye haiz nahin. jab haiz aaye to namaz padhna chhod dey, jab khatam ho jaey to apney jism sey khoon ko dho dal aur (ghusl kar key) namaz ada kar. ye hadees Wakee ki hai."
622,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey taweel arsey tak ba-kasrat istihaza aata raha tha. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui taake aap ko (apni kaifiyat) bata kar masla malum karun. mujhey apni behan Zenab (Raziallahu anha) key ghar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mil gaey. mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey aap sey eik kaam hai. aap ney farmaya : aey khatoon ! kya kaam hai? mainey kaha : mujhey taweel arsey tak b-kasrat istihaza aata rehta hai jiski wajeh sey main namaz, roza ada nahin kar sakti, to aap mujhey kya hukm detey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main terey liye rui tajwiz karta hun, kyonkey wo khoon ko jazb kar leti hai. mainey kaha : wo to us sey ziyada hai. padhi. uskey baad Raavi ney puri hadees Shareek ki hadees ki tarah bayan ki."
623,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : eik aurat ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya, usney kaha : mujhey istihaza aata hai to main pak hi nahin hoti. to kya main namaz chhod dun? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin jitney din raat tujhey (bimari shuru honey sey pehley har maah) haiz aaya karta tha itney arse tak (namaz) chhod diya kar. Abu-Bakar (bin Abu Sahiba) ki eik riwayat mein yun hai : is miqdaar key mutabiq mahiney mein sey, uskey baad ghusl kar ley aur langot baandh ley phir namaz padh ley."
624,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Fatima binte Abu Habeesh‬ (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey istihaza ki shikayat hai, isliye main pak nahin hoti , to kya main namaz chhod dun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin, wo to (bimari ki) eik rag hai. ye haiz (ka khoon) nahin. haiz key dinon (dinon) mein namaz sey ijtinab (bacha) kar, iskey baad ghusl kar ley aur har namaz key liye wuzu kar liya kar, agar-che chataai par khoon tapakta rahey."
625,"Hazrat Adi bin Sabit Ansari (Rahimahullah) apney walid sey, aur wo Adi key nana Hazrat Abdullah bin Yazeed Khutmi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : istihaza wali aurat haiz key dinon (dinon) mein namaz chhod dey, phir ghusl kar ley aur har namaz key liye wuzu karey aur rozey bhi rakhey, namaz bhi padhey."
626,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Umme-Habiba binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) jo Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya thin, saat saal istihaza ki bimari mein mubtala rahin. (aakhir kaar) unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey shikayat ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye haiz nahin, ye to (bimari ki) eik rag hai. jab haiz aaye to namaz chhod dey aur jab khatam ho jaey to ghusl kar key namaz padh. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : chunanche wo har namaz key liye ghusl kiya karti thin. wo apni behan (Ummul-momenin) Zenab binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) key tab mein (pani dal kar ghusl key liye) beth jatin yahan tak key khoon ki surkhi pani par aa jati."
627,"Hazrat Hamna binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein unhen istihazey ki bimari thi. unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : mujhey bahut buri tarah shadeed istihaza aata hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : rui rakh liya karo . unhoney kaha : wo to us sey ziyada shadeed hai. wo to behta hi chala jata hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : langot baandh liya karo aur Allah key ilm par aitimad kar key har mahiney chhe saat din haiz shumar kar lo. phir ghusl kar lo aur teyis-chaubees din namaz roza ada karo. Zohar ko der sey aur Asr ko jaldi padh lo, aur un dono (namazon) key liye eik baar ghusl kar liya karo . (isi tarah) maghrib ki namaz der sey aur Isha ki namaz jaldi padh liya karo, aur in dono key liye eik baar ghusl karo aur ye tariqa mujhey ziyada pasand hai."
628,"Hazrat Umme Qais binte Mohsin (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey kapdey ko haiz ka khoon lag janey ka masla poochha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey beeri key patton aur pani key sath dho dalo, aur usey khurch do, chahey lakdi sey khurcho."
629,"Hazrat Asma binte Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey kapdey ko lag janey waley haiz key khoon key barey mein sawal kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : ungliyon sey mal kar dho ley aur usey pehan kar namaz padh ley."
630,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum mein sey kisi ko haiz aata tha to pak honey par wo ungliyon sey mal kar kapdey sey khoon utaar deti thi, phir (wahan sey) kapda dho leti, aur baqi kapdey par chheentey maar leti aur usey pehan kar namaz padh leti thi."
631,"Hazrat Muaaza Adwiya(Reh. Aleh.) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey eik aurat ney sawal kiya : kya haiz wali aurat namaz ki qaza degi? Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney us sey kaha : kya to haroori (khaariji) hai? hamein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein haiz aata tha, phir hum pak ho jati thin, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein (kabhi) namaz ki qaza deney ka hukm nahin farmaya."
632,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : mujhey masjid mein sey musalla (jaey-namaz) utha do. mainey arz kiya : main haiz sey hun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara haiz tumharey haath main to nahin hai."
633,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein aetikaf bethey huye they aur main haiz sey hoti thi to aap apna sar Mubarak merey qarib kar detey chunanche main sar dho deti aur kanghi kar deti thi."
634,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri god mein sar rakh kar Quran Majeed ki tilawat kar letey they, jabke main haiz sey hoti thi."
635,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum (Ummehaatul Momeneen) mein sey koi jab khas dinon (haaiz) mein hoti to khoon ki shiddat aur kasrat key dinon (din) mein bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey izaar baandhney ko kehtey, phir us sey mubashrat farmatey (jism key sath jism mila kar let jatey) (lekin) tum mein sey kisi ko apni khahish par itna qabu hai jitna qabu Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apni khahish par hasil tha?"
636,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum (Ummehaatul Momeneen) mein sey koi jab dinon (haiz) sey hoti to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey teh band baandh leney ka hukm detey, phir us sey mubashrat (boss aur kinaar) farmatey."
637,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath aap key lihaaf mein (leti hui) thi, mujhey haiz shuru honey ka ehsas huwa. jis tarah aurton ko hota hai. main aahisatagi key sath lihaaf sey nikal gaee, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tumhen khoon aa gaya hai? mainey kaha : mujhey haiz ki wo kaifiyat mehsus hui hai jo aurton ko hoti hai. aap ney farmaya : ye chiz to Allah ney Adam ki betiyon par likh di hai. Ummul-mominin ney farmaya : main khamoshi sey uth gaee aur apni haalat ko durust kiya. phir wapis aai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : lihaaf mein merey paas aa jao. unhoney kaha chunanche mainey bhi aap key sath lihaaf ley liya."
638,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) (aur apni hamsheera (bahan)) Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey sawal kiya : aap ka haiz ke dinon mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath uthna bethna kis tarah hota tha? unhoney farmaya : jab hum (azwaaje mutah'raat (paak biwiyon)) mein sey kisi ko haiz shuru hota to wo nisf (aadhi) raanon tak chadar lapet leti, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath let jati."
639,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney haiz wali aurat sey mubashrat (sohbat) ki, ya aurat ki peeth mein mubashrat (sohbat) ki, ya kisi kaahin key paas gaya (aur us sey ghaibi maamlat key barey mein kuchh poochha) aur uski kahi hui baat ko sach maan liya to usney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par nazil ki janey wali chiz key sath kufr kiya."
640,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke haiz ke dinon mein aurat sey mubashrat karney waley key barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo eik Dinar ya nisf (aadha) Dinar sadqa dey.
641,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke wo haiz sey farigh huin to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney baal khol do aur ghusl karo. Ali bin Muhammad ki riwayat mein hai : apna sar khol do.
642,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Asma (binte Shakal Ansaariya (Raziallahu anha)) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey haiz key ghusl key barey mein masla puchha to aap ney farmaya : aurat ko chahiye ke pani aur beeri key pattey ley ley, phir safai karey aur achchhi tarah safai karey. ya farmaya : bahut ziyada safai karey (jism ko khub saaf karey), phir sar par pani dal kar khub maley yahan tak key pani baalon ki jadon tak pahunch jaaey. phir sarey badan par pani bahaaey phir rui ka khushbudar phohaa ley kar us sey tahaarat kerey. Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : main uskey sath kaisey tahaarat hasil karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Subhan Allah ! uskey sath tahaarat karo. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney aahista sey kaha is ko khoon key maqam par laga. Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ghusle-janabat (sambhog ke bad napaki ke ghusl) key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : aurat ko chahiye ke pani ley, phir safai karey aur achi tarah safai kerey. ya farmaya : bahut ziyada safai kerey. phir sar par pani dal kar maley yahan tak key pani baalon ki jadon tak pahunch jaey. phir apney jism par pani baha ley. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : ansaar ki aurten bhi bahut achchhi aurten thin. unhein Deen key masaayel seekhney sey haya rukawat nahin hoti thi."
643,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main haiz ke dinon mein hoti thi to (baaz oqaat aisa bhi hota tha ke) main haddi wali boti sey daanton key sath gosht nochti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us (boti) ko ley letey aur jahan mainey munh lagaya tha, wahin sey munh laga kar us haddi sey gosht nochte, main bartan mein pani peeti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahin munh rakh (kar pani pi) letey jahan mainey munh rakha hota tha."
644,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Yahudi ghar mein haaiza aurat key paas nahin bethtey they, na (uskey sath mil kar) khatey peetey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey is baat ka zikr kiya gaya (aur masla daryaft kiya gaya) to Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farma di : (وَيَسْأَلُونَكَ عَنْ الْمَحِيضِ قُلْ هُوَ أَذًى فَاعْتَزِلُوا النِّسَاءَ فِي الْمَحِيضِ) ""aur aap sey haiz key barey mein poochhtey hain, farma dijiye, wo gandagi hai, so tum haiz (key dinon) mein aurton sey alag raho. (iski wazahat kartey huye) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum jima (sambhog) key siwa sab kuchh kar saktey ho."
645,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us masjid key sehan mein dakhil huye aur buland aawaz sey aelan farmaya : kisi junbi (samhog ke bad napaaki ki halat mein insan) ya haaiza ko masjid mein dakhil hona jayez nahin."
646,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us aurat key barey mein, jisey pak honey key baad koi mashkook (shak wali) chiz nazar aaye, farmaya : wo eik rag hai. 'ya farmaya : wo ragein hain. Muhammad bin Yahyaa ney kaha : pak honey key baad sey murad ghusl key baad hai."
647,"Hazrat Umme Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum zard aur matyaley pani ko kuchh nahin samajhti thin. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney kaha , hamein Muhammad bin Yahyaa ney Muhammad bin Abdullah Raqaashi sey ba-wasta Wuhaib an Ayub, Hazrat Umme Atiya sey bayan kiya, unhoney kaha : hum zard aur matyaley pani ko kuch nahin samajhti thin. Muhammad bin Yahyaa ney kaha is hadees ko bayan karney mein wuhaib hamarey nazdik (Maamar sey) ziyada qabile aitimad hain."
648,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamanae Mubarak mein nifaas wali aurat chaalis din bethi rehti thi, aur hum chhaiyon ka ilaj karney key liye chehron par waras lagaati thin."
649,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney nifaas wali aurat key liye chaalis din ki miqdaar muqarrar ki hai, siwaye uskey ke us muddat sey pehley tuhur (paaki) nazar aa jaey."
650,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab koi shakhs haiz ki haalat mein biwi sey mubashrat (sohbat) kar leta to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey aadha Dinar sadqa karney ka hukm detey they."
651,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey haaiza key sath mil kar khana khaney ka hukm daryaft kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uskey sath mil kar kha liya karo."
652,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz padh rahey they aur main aap key qarib (leti hui) thi jabke main haiz sey thi. mainey eik chadar apney ooper ley rakhi thi aur uska eik hissa aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key jism Mubarak par tha."
653,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (ghar mein nafl) namaz padhi . aap ney chadar odh rakhi thi jis ka kuchh hissa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par tha aur kuchh hissa un par tha. aur wo haalate haiz mein thin."
654,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey ghar tashrif laye to un ki eik azad karda londi chhup gaee, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey haiz aa gaya hai? Ummul-mominin ney kaha : ji haan. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni pagdi key kapdey mein sey phaad kar eik hissa usey diya aur farmaya : isey odhni bana lo."
655,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala kisi baligh aurat ki namaz odhni key baghair qubul nahin karta."
656,"Hazrat Muaaza (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey sawal kiya, kya haiz wali aurat mahndi (ya koi doosra khizaab) laga sakti hai? Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas hoten aur khizaab laga leti thin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen mana nahin farmatey they."
657,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : meri eik kalaai toot gaee, mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha to aap ney mujhey pattiyon par masah karney ka hukm diya.(Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid) Abul-Hasan bin Salma ney kaha, unhen Dubri ney Abdur-Razzaaq sey sabiqa riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
658,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke Hazrat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhuma) ko kandhey par uthaya huwa tha, aur unka lu'aab beh kar aap par gir raha tha."
659,"Hazrat Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey dekha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein (pani ka) dol hazir kiya gaya, aap ney is mein sey pani ley kar kulli ki, phir dol mein kulli ki jo kastoori ki tarah ya kastoori sey pakizah tar thi aur aap ney dol sey bahar naak saaf ki."
660,Imam Zohri ney Hazrat Mehmood bin Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat bayan ki aur ye wo Sahaba hain jinhen wo kulli yad thi jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik dol mein ki thi jis mein unkey eik kunwen sey pani liya gaya tha.
661,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi aurat , dusri aurat key satar ko na dekhey, aur koi mard kisi mard key satar ko na dekhey."
662,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sharmgaah ko kabhi nahin dekha. Abu-Bakar ney kaha : Aubu Nuaim (Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key ghulam ki bajaey) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki londi sey bayan kiya kartey they."
663,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ghusle-janabat (sambhog ke bad naapaaki ka gusl) kiya, phir aap ko thodi si jagah (khushk) nazar aai jisey pani nahin pahuncha tha. chunanche aap ney apney baalon ko us jagah par nichod kar tar kar liya. Janab Is-haq ney apni hadees mein kaha ke aap ney apney baalon ko is par nichodaa."
664,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : mainey ghusle-janabat (sambhog ke bad naapaaki ka gusl) kiya aur Fajr ki namaz padhi. din chadha to mujhey eik nakhun key barabar jagah nazar aai jahan (ghusl key doran mein) pani nahin pahuncha tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar to us jagah (geelaa) haath pher deta to kafi hota.
665,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa , usney wuzu kiya tha aur nakhun key barabar jagah chhod di thi, wahan pani nahin pahuncha tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : wapis ja kar achchhi tarah wuzu karo."
666,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko dekha ke usney wuzu kiya (lekin) paon par eik nakhun key barabar jagah (khushk) chhod di. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey hukm diya ke dobara wuzu karey aur dobara namaz padhey. chunanche wo shakhs (wuzu karney key liye masjid sey) wapis chala gaya."
